PN,35501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FA Jersey family say they have been
OL,7,Fdenied their dream holiday and left
OL,8,F#5,000 out of pocket because an
OL,9,Fairline did not recognise the island
OL,10,Fon their passports.
OL,12,FIwona Izbinska-Sosnowska, along with
OL,13,Fher husband Andrzej and 19-year-old
OL,14,Fdaughter Ava, were supposed to fly
OL,15,Fwith China Eastern Airlines from
OL,16,FLondon Gatwick via Shanghai to Vietnam
OL,17,Ffor a three-week, once-in-a-lifetime
OL,18,Ftrip to Hanoi and H Long Bay.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FIt was much more than a holiday for
OL,7,Fthe family, as Iwona is in remission,
OL,8,Fhaving survived cancer twice and
OL,9,Fovercome years of treatment.
OL,11,FShe explains: "We have dreamed about
OL,12,Fthis opportunity for 15 years because
OL,13,Fof the history, the culture, and we
OL,14,Fhave never been to Asia, so adding
OL,15,FChina as a transit country was
OL,16,Fsomething special to us as well."
OL,18,FAndrzej has a Polish passport and did
OL,19,Fnot encounter any issues.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FHowever, Iwona says both she and Ava
OL,7,Fwere refused boarding by China Eastern
OL,8,Fcheck-in staff who would not accept
OL,9,Ftheir valid British passports because
OL,10,Fthey were issued in the Bailiwick of
OL,11,FJersey.
OL,13,FShe describes: "They asked us to wait
OL,14,Faside because on their system, there
OL,15,Fwas a note that there's no country
OL,16,Flike that.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,F"We tried to explain we are from
OL,7,FJersey in the Channel Islands, a Crown
OL,8,FDependency, and we are British
OL,9,FCitizens. Other British Citizens were
OL,10,Fallowed to board the plane without any
OL,11,Fvisas or problems."
OL,13,FIwona told ITV News that airline staff
OL,14,Fthen tried to assist the family for
OL,15,Ftwo hours as she frantically called
OL,16,Fauthorities in the UK, Jersey and the
OL,17,FVietnamese embassy in London, but no
OL,18,Fone was able to resolve the issue.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FIwona says Andrzej opted to stay
OL,7,Fbehind with his family and the plane
OL,8,Ftook off, leaving them "defeated" and
OL,9,F"distressed".
OL,11,FShe adds: "I feel I've been betrayed,
OL,12,FI don't know by whom, by the airline,
OL,13,Fthe system, it was so unfair.
OL,15,F"Jersey has the same benefits and
OL,16,Fconsular rights as British Citizens
OL,17,Ffrom London and the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,F"We have been checking for six months,
OL,7,Fwe had valid travel documents and
OL,8,Fquite new passports, so everything was
OL,9,Freally well prepared. I don't know
OL,10,Fwhat else we could have done.
OL,12,F"We should receive the same support as
OL,13,Fother British people and it was like
OL,14,Fgrief, we're still emotional."
OL,16,FThe family made a claim on their
OL,17,FAllianz travel insurance, but were
OL,18,Fdenied any compensation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FThe firm told ITV News that "policies
OL,7,Fcover a defined set of circumstances"
OL,8,Fand "in this case, the situation does
OL,9,Fnot fall within the events covered".
OL,11,FIwona says they were told they would
OL,12,Fhave to sue China Eastern Airlines
OL,13,Findependently to recover their losses.
OL,15,FShe explains: "It's sometimes not
OL,16,Fabout the money. We are not young and
OL,17,Fafter I've suffered so much with the
OL,18,Fcancer, I may not have any other
OL,19,Fopportunity to go for such a long trip.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,F"This was that moment that we were
OL,7,Fready for and it was shattered, we are
OL,8,Fgrieving really."
OL,10,FIwona is calling on the new Government
OL,11,Fof Jersey to do more so "other
OL,12,Ffamilies will not go through this" and
OL,13,Fhopes "something will be done very
OL,14,Fquickly".
OL,16,FA spokesperson for Jersey's External
OL,17,FRelations Ministry told ITV News that
OL,18,Fthey are "aware of this unusual case
OL,19,Fand are working as a matter of urgency
OL,20,Fto ensure it is not repeated".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1782730080
OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FThe spokesperson adds: "We have
OL,7,Freceived confirmation from the Chinese
OL,8,Fauthorities that British Citizens
OL,9,Fholding Jersey-issued passports are
OL,10,Feligible for visa-free travel to China
OL,11,Funder the same conditions as those
OL,12,Fholding UK-issued passports."
OL,14,FThe Ministry say they are working with
OL,15,Fthe UK Foreign Office and the Chinese
OL,16,FEmbassy in London to "ensure that the
OL,17,Fcorrect information is passed to
OL,18,Fairlines".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
