OL,3,CFamily denied dream holiday as airline
OL,4,C'didn't know Jersey existed'
OL,6,FITV News has contacted China Eastern
OL,7,FAirlines and the UK Foreign Office for
OL,8,Fcomment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/10
